g.text: PrometheusTime series database▪ Enables scraping of metrics from pods▪ Retrieves log data from Loki▪ Retrieves trace data from Tempo▪ Provides data to Grafana
GrafanaData visualizer▪ Reads log, metric and trace data from Prometheus▪ Provides powerful tools for data visualization
PromtailLog scraper▪ Scrapes and labels log data from pods▪ Pushes log data to Loki
EBS CSI ControllerPersistent volume provider▪ Creates AWS Elastic Block Store upon request and connects it to pods
ArgoCDContinuous Deployment Provider▪ Synchronizes k8s state with a Git repository▪ Enables rollback of state based on commit history▪ Provides superficial administration of cluster applications
DexOAuth2 as a Cognito handler▪ Handles authentication for ArgoCD▪ Handles authentication for Grafana
